Description: Provides access to meteorological observations, forecasts,
    alerts and climatology data from the Spanish Meteorological Agency
    (AEMET) through the 'AEMET OpenData' API <https://opendata.aemet.es/>.
    Includes tools for working with tabular and spatial data and for
    creating Walter-Lieth climate diagrams, warming stripes and wind
    roses.
